{"tid":1435456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］唔好失焦，要抗衡政府記者會","createTime":"2019-08-09T05:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:03:52.000Z","uid":158417,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67417fc973ad92c875332bb7ed14c23a5cfb8bcc","tid":1435456,"uid":158417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:07:21.000Z","msg":"雖然政府同警犬的記者會好多野笑，但同2014一樣，呢個係政府想轉移視線的方法，將我地的焦點放喺恥笑高官警犬度，同時再將革命港獨帽子扣喺示威者身上。所以，我地需要搵方法去形象化返我地敵人真正的面目，對準政權！<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到有兩樣野可以做：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">1. 幫政府計算每次搞記者會要用的公帑，喺連儂牆宣傳</span><br />\n每日update累積計算，成班高官警察咁高人工，比d淺藍睇下政府每日燒左幾多立稅人的錢去搞記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">2. 整個list列出政府每日喺記者會公佈1-2個荒謬/不合真相/不回應的話題或說法</span><br />\n每日update，繼續請記者朋友死纏要求政府回應。list入面列出的話題或說法不可刪除，除非政府認錯或者有一個民間可以接受的說法。相信個表會愈來愈長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一點配合埋第二點，再加上文宣，可以比民眾親眼睇到政府點樣浪費立稅人的錢搞d垃圾記者會<br />\n<br />\n咁做希望可以幫到自己人對準問題唔玩膠化同拉攏到一d淺藍，或者至少令淺藍唔會變左支持政府<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴絲有咩睇法呢？"},{"pid":"7b9b744de3292db87d6247b3aff62061733a6648","tid":1435456,"uid":52566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DUUxQ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DUUxQ0.jpg&h=ca7950a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCTNSQ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCTNSQ4.jpg&h=d6b6e3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9XSjv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9XSjv7.jpg&h=517cb078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iE9hvCP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiE9hvCP.jpg&h=fd6ea43a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jUSiZwc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjUSiZwc.jpg&h=